                                              "is_correct":  false,
                                              "feedback":  "Homework is not identified as the next best alternative in this question."
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "id":  "B",
                                              "text":  "The money earned from working",
                                              "is_correct":  false,
                                              "feedback":  "The money earned is a benefit of the chosen option, not the opportunity cost."
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "id":  "C",
                                              "text":  "The value of attending the game",
                                              "is_correct":  true,
                                              "feedback":  "Correct. The opportunity cost is the value of the next best option that was given up."
